{"tid":195619,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚野叫異常冷靜咁撳電話？","createTime":"2017-04-10T17:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T17:50:16.000Z","uid":96628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"814f2103e523918d056c3894b9d152a6e3a95dd1","tid":195619,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"屌你啦廢老，<br />\n壞車唔撳電話可以做乜鳩？<br />\n唔可以讚下香港人好有秩序？<br />\n屌你老母乜撚野叫&quot;異常冷靜&quot;？<br />\n唔撚可以係正面啲咁讚人冷靜？<br />\n日本人嗰次唔撚話人&quot;異常如戇鳩般的冷靜&quot;？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BD24F4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBD24F4d.png&h=21b9acda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔通好撚似你班廢閪咁驚到鳩縮咩，<br />\n我相信好多人撳電話都會係不斷update網上新聞，<br />\n話哂自己黑munmun果撚住喺架車到，死撚左人都唔知，<br />\n唔通要好似啲蝗咁亂鳩咁叫亂鳩咁人踩人咩屌你老母！<br />\n唔讚下大家都好冷靜？<br />\n越睇越嬲，<br />\n好心啲人唔好用啲咁嘅字眼再分化啲香港人，乜都屌屌屌，<br />\n可唔可以讚下啲香港人比啲正能量大家？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170410/s00001/1491829632866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170410%2Fs00001%2F1491829632866&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b0f3c601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170410%2Fs00001%2F1491829632866&h=708d1b65\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170410/s00001/1491829632866</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170410/s00001/70a99afdb8326af3c8962a37541bcdf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170410%2Fs00001%2F70a99afdb8326af3c8962a37541bcdf1.jpg&h=cff50165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《明報》聯絡到當時正身處由九龍灣開往彩虹方向列車的乘客張先生。張先生憶述他約晚上6時06分他登上該列車，準備前往長沙灣，列車甫駛離九龍灣車站、尚未駛入隧道時，突然傳來「轟」一聲，車廂的空調及電視訊號同時停止運作，車廂內一半燈光熄滅。當列車駛至隧道時便突然停下，其後傳出重複的廣播稱「列車服務稍為延遲」。<br />\n<br />\n張先生說，數分鐘後車廂內突然一片漆黑，「大部分人異常冷靜咁撳電話」或致電家人報平安，後來車廂內甚為焗促，有乘客終忍不住打開車窗。<br />\n<br />\n張先生等待時感到有點不安，開始思疑不只他所乘的列車出事，亦不斷聽到疑似啟動機電裝置的聲音。接近晚上7時，漆黑之中列車的車頭緊急逃生門終開啟，他與其他乘客一起排隊走落路軌，安全步回月台。其間他見到多名救護員攜同擔架牀到場救援，現場消息指是有孕婦感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: [url]<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170410/s00001/1491829632866#sthash.pSdZ39AH.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170410%2Fs00001%2F1491829632866%23sthash.pSdZ39AH.dpuf&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=8d8295b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170410%2Fs00001%2F1491829632866%23sthash.pSdZ39AH.dpuf&h=2bac43a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170410/s00001/1491829632866#sthash.pSdZ39AH.dpuf</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"94a52e4c145f63d19c13486b05ca09504b8ca93f","tid":195619,"uid":65425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}